text: Pycnandra fillipes is a species of plant in the family Sapotaceae. It is endemic to New Caledonia and has two subspecies: subsp. fillipes and subsp. multiflora. ==References== * Jaffré, T. et al. 1998. Leptostylis gatopensis. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 22 August 2007.
